description.en:
We believe you should own your own genome, the DNA blueprint of what makes you who you are, so we built GenomesDAO. 

GenomesDAO is a private and secure DNA data bank that puts you back in control of your genome utilising AMD SVS-ES Vault and blockchain technology.  By addressing privacy, security and ownership concerns of DNA testing and sharing, we are building the world’s largest user-owned genomic data bank to secure the future of personalised medicine.

$GNOME is the GenomesDAO governance token. Holders can influence decisions concerning the project such as proposing or deciding on new feature proposals and even changing the governance system itself.
